  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个订单状态流转图。核心状态有四个：OPEN（待处理）、CONFIRMED（已确认）、COMPLETED（已完成）、CANCELLED（已取消）。起点是OPEN，终点有两个——COMPLETED和CANCELLED都可以结束流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OPEN",
        "CONFIRMED",
        "COMPLETED",
        "CANCELLED",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那OPEN之后能直接到CANCELLED吗？还是必须先经过CONFIRMED才能取消？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OPEN",
        "CANCELLED",
        "CONFIRMED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "两种情况都可以。用户下单后还没付款时可以取消，进入CONFIRMED之后也能取消。所以OPEN到CANCELLED要连一条线，CONFIRMED到CANCELLED也要连。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OPEN",
        "CANCELLED",
        "CONFIRMED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把四个状态和起点终点画出来，然后连上OPEN到CONFIRMED、OPEN到CANCELLED、CONFIRMED到COMPLETED、CONFIRMED到CANCELLED这几条线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OPEN",
        "CONFIRMED",
        "COMPLETED",
        "CANCELLED",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，COMPLETED之后还能取消吗？比如售后退款的情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPLETED",
        "CANCELLED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我查了一下需求文档，COMPLETED是终态，售后走另外的流程。所以COMPLETED和CANCELLED都直接连到终点[*]，但COMPLETED和CANCELLED之间不加连线。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPLETED",
        "CANCELLED",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个逻辑。COMPLETED和CANCELLED都是结束状态，各自指向终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPLETED",
        "CANCELLED",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。最终状态图：起点指向OPEN，OPEN可转到CONFIRMED或CANCELLED，CONFIRMED可转到COMPLETED或CANCELLED，COMPLETED和CANCELLED都指向终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
